                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 137.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 16<hi rend="italic">th June</hi>, 1845, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months</hi>)—I was at his trial—he is the man.</p>
